Class DefaultParametersErrorHandler

java.lang.Object
com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.deser.DeserializationProblemHandler
uk.co.spudsoft.params4j.impl.DefaultParametersErrorHandler
public class DefaultParametersErrorHandler extends com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.deser.DeserializationProblemHandler
The default handler of errors reported by Jackson. This error handler logs the errors (at 'warn' level) and then ignores them.
Author:
jtalbut
